    <p><ul id="patient_overview"><li><a href="/english/COPDengels" title="COPD"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/torso.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="COPD"/></a><h1><a href="/english/COPDengels" title="COPD">COPD</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/english/COPDengels">COPD is an incurable pulmonary disease in which breathing becomes increasingly difficult.</a></div><a href="/english/COPDengels"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li><li><a href="/english/genes-engels" title="Genes"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/dna.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="Genes"/></a><h1><a href="/english/genes-engels" title="Genes">Genes</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/english/genes-engels">Genes are the carriers of characteristics. What does this mean, and why is genetic research so important with regard to COPD?</a></div><a href="/english/genes-engels"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li><li><a href="/english/copacetic-engels" title="COPACETIC study"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/stethoscope.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="COPACETIC study"/></a><h1><a href="/english/copacetic-engels" title="COPACETIC study">COPACETIC study</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/english/copacetic-engels">COPACETIC is an international study of the origin and course of COPD.</a></div><a href="/english/copacetic-engels"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li><li><a href="/english/the-researchers-engels" title="The researchers"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/doctor.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="The researchers"/></a><h1><a href="/english/the-researchers-engels" title="The researchers">The researchers</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/english/the-researchers-engels">A wide range of European researchers is collaborating on this project. </a></div><a href="/english/the-researchers-engels"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li><li><a href="/english/participating-countries" title="Participating countries"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/flag.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="Participating countries"/></a><h1><a href="/english/participating-countries" title="Participating countries">Participating countries</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/english/participating-countries">Different countries in Europe collaborate in this project.</a></div><a href="/english/participating-countries"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li><li><a href="/research" title="Research website"><img src="/images/library//pictograms/copacetic.jpg" width="245" height="125" class="" alt="Research website"/></a><h1><a href="/research" title="Research website">Research website</a></h1><div class="intro"><div class="intro_content"><a href="/research">Click on this link to go to the international website for researchers. </a></div><a href="/research"><div class="intro_image">&#160;</div></a></div></li></ul></p>    </div>
